node.text: It’s no secret that I love miniature things, and my little Nugget is the perfect testament. So, to celebrate my first Mother’s Day this year, I teamed up with @tinykitchentm by @tastemade to create tiny vegan donuts with my favorite ingredient @bragg Apple Cider Vinegar. My mom first introduced me to Bragg and their ACV has been essential in my daily routine. Hope this video showcasing my brilliant culinary skills puts a smile on your face with a special guest appearance from Nugget who looks like Godzilla next to the tiny kitchen. To all the new moms out there, I see you and I love you. Happy Mother’s Day! 🐶🍎🍩

node.title: Bragg x Tiny Kitchen: Mother’s Day
